---
name: intent_parser
temperature: 0.0
response_format: json
---

Parse the user's financial question to determine what data to fetch.

## User message
"{{message}}"

## Today's date
{{today}}

## Response (JSON only)
{
  "intent": "<spending_query|income_query|budget_query|comparison|forecast|general>",
  "date_range": {
    "start": "<YYYY-MM-DD>",
    "end": "<YYYY-MM-DD>"
  },
  "categories": ["<category name if mentioned, else empty array>"],
  "merchants": ["<merchant name if mentioned, else empty array>"],
  "aggregation": "<daily|weekly|monthly|total>",
  "requires_trend": <boolean>
}

## Examples
"bulan ini aku paling boros di mana?" →
{ "intent": "spending_query", "date_range": {"start": "2024-01-01", "end": "2024-01-31"}, "categories": [], "aggregation": "total", "requires_trend": false }

"pengeluaran makan minggu ini berapa?" →
{ "intent": "spending_query", "date_range": { ... this week ... }, "categories": ["Makanan"], "aggregation": "total", "requires_trend": false }
